    "Thereafter, the students in the study group were subjected to a four-week series of activities implemented by the course instructor.",
    "An abrupt shift from in-person classes to emergency distance education was mandated by the Council of Higher Education due to a devastating earthquake in Turkey.",
    "Therefore, this study and interviews were conducted online.",
    "Students participated in online classes using Microsoft Teams, while interview sessions were conducted using Zoom.",
    "To schedule the interviews, participants were initially asked to fill out a Google Form to indicate their preferences."
